ActRoyal Canadian Mint Act
PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Transport of J. MARC BRÛLÉ of Manotick, Ontario, as a director of the Board of Directors of the Royal Canadian Mint to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years, in the place of Paul H. Bilodeau, whose term has expired.
